<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200902/c70f447ab70e4d0f8ee4c179bcad0438.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right">组图：李锋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/510e0bd6e6d34a11802f9729dea10b52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200902/dcc9c1ff882a4d81a4a3515de368df09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
